<h2>Companion plugin integrations</h2>

<p>The Unified Grader is opinionated about what should live inside the
plugin and what should be borrowed from elsewhere. The integrations on
this page are optional — if the partner plugin isn't installed, the
relevant UI is simply hidden. Nothing on this list is required for core
grading to work.</p>

